These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
House: victorian, art-deco, modern
1. the modern house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
2. the modern house is between the victorian house and the art-deco house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| House   | victorian | modern | art-deco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
City: rome, nizza, prague
1. the person traveling to rome is between the person traveling to nizza and the person traveling to prague##2
2. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| City   | prague | rome | nizza |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
City: paris, liverpool, colone
1. the person traveling to liverpool is between the person traveling to paris and the person traveling to colone##2
2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| City   | colone | liverpool | paris |

