.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda, cola
1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking mirinda and the person drinking lemonade##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| Beverage   | lemonade | cola | mirinda |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, metal, ambient
1. the fan electronic is between the fan ambient and the fan metal##2
2. the fan ambient is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | metal | electronic | ambient |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-6::.
